name: SHADOWS
description:
When I try to sleep I start to hear their voices inside my room, I can't see them but I know they are there. I'm terrified, they want to hurt me, it's torture, I need help, I feel their hands on me. I close my eyes in the hope that they will disappear and I can have some peace in my life, some tranquillity, some happiness. I just want them to get out of here, I think I deserve it, I'm old and tired, but having killed them doesn't give them the right to disturb me, does it?
